                        span Zeugitania, Carthage; c. 350-320 BC,
                            | Stater, 9.31g. Jenkins-Group IIIf, 37.
                            | Obv: Head of Tanit l., wreathed with wheat,
                            | wearing necklace of pendants and triple-drop earring.
                            | Rx: Horse standing r. on exergual line; group
