                            | of Carthage are far more artistic and struck
                            | in higher relief than the electrum staters.
                            | This is no exception . Choice EF
                .item-card-main-block-title
                    .item-card-main-block-title-header
                        span Gordian I Africanus. Sestertius
                        <svg width="30" height="28" viewBox="0 0 30 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
